message.body: Hey pretty lady! What are you up tonight?
I'm going to be in red hook all day if you want to grab a coffee or drink later

Good luck with your art show this weekend
Yeah let's do it, ill come to red hook
Or maybe Greenpoint where you are staying
Yes please! Oh thanks lady. I'll call you when I'm done with work maybe like seven ish?

Or we can do a bar in red hook
We decide later Have fun camping. Yay
